Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:06.58,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.99,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:17.31,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:52.62,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Come one, come all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:55.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't buy one today, your Christmas cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.39,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,How about that? It turned into a plain old cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:01.15,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's hip with today's youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:03.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If you buy one now, it comes with a reindeer mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You there! Yes, you, beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Damned adventurers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:18.78,Title,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1506,1)}A Lost Child at Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A Lost Child at Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:22.28,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:27.67,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,When Akatsuki wakes up, \NHenrietta will contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:28.29,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:31.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:33.76,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've been standing by the window for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.05,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:43.18,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to where I used to live, it's cold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.93,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't born in Akihabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.62,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in a town called Kiyose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.15,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, it would be around Nobidome District.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.61,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a noble, Rieze?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:59.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:02.16,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in a small, normal home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:08.24,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.77,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,About you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.93,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,No, about Akatsuki or Henrietta, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:16.67,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Or Marielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:18.27,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.67,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:21.52,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.55,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.67,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's that I never tried to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.27,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Not even about Crusty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's especially cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.19,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In school, I was a good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:41.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers loved me, \Nand I was adept at my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:46.47,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,When I showed how clever I was, \Neveryone praised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I became skilled at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I joined D.D.D. when I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I met a lot of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:04.47,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and I was forced to realize that the only \Nworld I had ever tried to see was so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:12.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't, I may have gone on like that forever, \Nwith something very important missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.48,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I was really on a bad path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:17.98,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:21.57,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What's most important is always there, somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.47,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,And because it's important,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.74,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I think you need to treasure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.49,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.10,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,well, to be a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:36.50,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm never good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.31,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.99,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to treat you properly, Rieze!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:47.01,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I won't have the right \Nto be treated kindly by you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.02,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,or to delude myself into thinking I'm protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.77,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Treat me properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.48,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.75,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Then here's my first bit of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:03.29,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,To treat someone "properly" is too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.86,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends, Lenessia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.52,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an adventurer, but if you don't mind that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.51,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,No... This couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.69,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:57.83,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Being pushed, rushed, driven along...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.33,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I trying to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:29.20,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I may not have a destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:33.56,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it would be so quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:37.83,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:46.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Something disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Did you also feel it, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.85,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:27.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't snow, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:28.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.17,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The memory fragments they offered up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,so they could rise up once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You were defeated, Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.60,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.71,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.36,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I had almost figured something out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:59.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:02.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:08.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a heck of a Christmas Eve, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:19.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I was naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't trust them enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:26.03,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that I'm upset because I couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do the best you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do what you needed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:37.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.20,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is it only a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:51.06,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sure it's because I wanted to see my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.30,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted him to pat me on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:59.19,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can find that which I almost found,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.64,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,if I search for it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.74,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I will, too, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:10.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.78,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:49.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I passed through some quiet place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.30,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.15,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.58,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I found something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:02.97,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,like I understand something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.41,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,So there's something I should do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.66,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Something I must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.63,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.38,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any scars, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.80,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.97,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:25.47,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was about time for you to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.03,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I know this isn't an appropriate request,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:33.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like you all to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:36.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Would you share your Teachings with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:39.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to capture that murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:44.17,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Nazuna, didn't Soujirou use the Teachings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:44.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.00,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.81,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you seek them, despite that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.10,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.54,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to end the murders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.49,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And not just your Teachings, but... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:04.76,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a way to stop him, \Nplease tell me anything you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.86,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:10.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:13.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,but I have to do something to end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:16.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,With my lord gone, someone has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.35,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.03,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We were asked to keep it a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.37,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,but that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.91,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, Shiro is away from Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.34,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.40,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you're so desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.04,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.91,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:43.33,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can end this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.18,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:06.20,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You half-passed, I would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:11.20,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,There are eight Teachings \Nthat D.D.D. is aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:14.20,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I've already gained my lord's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.48,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,He's told me to share them with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.21,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.48,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,To come all this way, just to start \Nover as a middle schooler...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.58,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem there are any more \Ngoblins over here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.23,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.22,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.58,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.74,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,I am, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.30,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.74,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,I've dealt with it all this time, and I'm still bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.03,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.91,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, my weapon's been acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.86,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Why not send it to be repaired?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:01.71,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.50,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not any less powerful, \Nso I've just overlooked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.71,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is "Disaster," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:13.01,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Its flavor text is pretty dark, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.89,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.28,SignA,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Onigiri Shop Enmusubi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.97,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:33.28,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Research announcements are always tense, \Nno matter how often you do them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.90,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like everyone was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:41.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,For one of Roderic Research's recent \Nannouncements, it had a lot of impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:46.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That now everyone can cook, \Neven if their sub-class isn't chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:50.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's limited to simple stuff like salad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:54.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But why is a change like this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Guild master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.85,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can keep eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Our investigation's interim reports are in, \Nso I'll just briefly interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:10.73,SignB,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Personality \N\N{\c&H805DAD&}Woman             {\c&HAAA96E&}Man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:10.73,SignE,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Voice \N\NSex Differences
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:07.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There are three things I need to announce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:10.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,First, regarding sex differences between \Nnow and when this was a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sex differences?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:15.50,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Some people play a different sex \Nthan they are in real life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.74,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:19.20,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,RDR has reported in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that personality is influenced by a person's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:26.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But it appears the voice is affected, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:29.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,An adventurer with a female \Nbody will find their voice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gradually becoming feminine,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:36.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,even if the player is actually a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:40.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Next is optical observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:44.75,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot we don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:48.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems the distance between \NAkihabara and Mt. Fuji is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:51.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the distance between any two points
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is increasing by a small amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.51,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.48,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that occurring everywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:03.78,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Yamato is getting bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.79,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Lastly, regarding flavor text...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, flavor text is merely
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.18,SignC,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Healing Potion (Basic)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.18,SignD,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Effect/ {\fs18}Healing Potion (Basic) \NRestores a small amount of HP
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an explanation that describes where \Nan item originated or what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.30,HUD1,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Explanation/ {\fs20}Healing Potion (Basic) \NA magical medicine created by adventurers. \NIts capabilities, flavor, and scent change \Ndepending on the skill of the creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.30,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,As the name suggests, it's just for flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.85,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It has no in-game effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.02,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.00,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,it's just to add atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:26.81,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:29.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It should have no meaning at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But we've confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that some items' flavor texts are \Nhaving real-world effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:43.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Could so many coincidences really occur at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:48.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we assume that this world \Nis undergoing some large-scale change?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.86,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Apocalypse is not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.02,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I've already heard the broader details.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:59.47,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer is a Person of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.97,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,You told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.54,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,If this gets out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,relations between adventurers and \NPeople of the Land will worsen in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:12.73,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki tried to resolve the situation \Nbecause she was concerned about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.12,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Though I can't imagine you'll be \Nable to hide it completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:24.43,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Not with all these victims...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:27.25,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Is the West Wind Brigade going public with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.98,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:31.40,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Souji said he's pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:34.16,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Though that's up to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.29,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:39.51,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop wasting time confirming things, \Nand get on with the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.47,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two were vain enough to think \Nyou could deal with this yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:51.27,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You knew you should have spoken to us, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:53.77,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being a little arrogant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:56.28,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you insulting the people around you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:59.28,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to remain alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.53,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's childish to tell yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that all you need is Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.54,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,True, it's always been that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.62,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I was content with how \Ncomfortable I felt in his shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.88,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I never tried to get close to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.71,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was totally reliant on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:20.05,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,When he left, I suddenly couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:23.05,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not even what he asked me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:27.42,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you've been \Ncoming here to protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.82,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who had the job of visiting Watermaple House.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.89,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I was, as well, and so was Rieze.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:40.49,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only one my lord relied on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.82,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.32,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:49.07,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I wanted to help her \Nbecause she was trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.33,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.60,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.10,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Rieze and I will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.59,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,But who should you be saying that to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.47,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki is my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:19.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Lenessia is doing her best,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.11,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.34,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of us... to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.32,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.50,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop that murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.01,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a friend, too, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:48.43,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, the sun has set.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.47,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.53,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,A broken spearhead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.10,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:57.79,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this is a training area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.90,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,For goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:20:59.82,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:04.32,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Surely not. I've never heard of them training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.45,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... It's acting strangely again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:16.58,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Sansa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:25.43,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.35,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:46.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:49.84,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The Graupel Sword Byakumaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.70,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the katana the samurai had?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.05,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:57.98,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it many times at Amenoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.42,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.46,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:05.97,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time, and I haven't gotten a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:10.81,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe and Naotsugu aren't playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:13.86,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,They won't always have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:15.48,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:19.48,Default - italics,M,0000,0000,0000,,Today, something just doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:22.75,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice anything else about the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:24.49,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:25.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:27.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:32.42,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:10.09,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer's mind is taken from him \Nas he becomes a true monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:13.64,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Is he remembering a legendary hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.64,0:24:16.42,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Rieze and Henrietta begin preparations for a raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.42,0:24:18.39,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki attempts to master the Teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:21.94,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,At some point, they find themselves \Nwith many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:24.40,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-six, in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:26.71,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Maidens of Watermaple.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:30.94,Title,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of Watermaple
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.71,0:24:28.70,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Rise up once more.
